00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(3,'Ahmad Fauzi','Photographer','template/assets/images/avata/3.jpg','Sebagai fotografer, saya sangat terbantu dengan rekomendasi spot-spot terbaik dari Yogyadrivertour. Hasil foto luar biasa!',5.00,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(4,'Dewi Lestari','Designer','template/assets/images/avata/4.jpg','Pengalaman cave tubing di Jomblang yang ditawarkan sangat seru! Tim yang profesional dan peralatan yang lengkap.',4.80,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(5,'Rizky Pratama','Student','template/assets/images/avata/5.jpg','Budget mahasiswa tapi bisa liburan seru di Yogyakarta! Terima kasih Yogyadrivertour untuk paket hematnya.',4.70,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'); /*!40000 ALTER TABLE `testimonials` ENABLE KEYS */; UNLOCK TABLES;  -- -- Table structure for table `tours` --  DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `tours`; /*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */; /*!50503 SET character_set_client = utf8mb4 */; CREATE TABLE `tours` (   `id` bigint unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,   `name` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,   `slug` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,   `description` text COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,   `short_description` text COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci,   `image` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,   `price` decimal(12,2) NOT NULL,   `discount_price` decimal(12,2) DEFAULT NULL,   `duration_days` int NOT NULL,   `duration_nights` int NOT NULL,   `max_participants` int NOT NULL,   `location` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,   `city` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Yogyakarta',   `asal_negara` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,   `category` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Adventure',   `tag` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,   `rating` decimal(3,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '5.00',   `review_count` int NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',   `is_featured` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',   `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',   `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,   `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,   PRIMARY KEY (`id`),   UNIQUE KEY `tours_slug_unique` (`slug`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci; /*!40101 SET character_set_client = @saved_cs_client */;  -- -- Dumping data for table `tours` --  LOCK TABLES `tours` WRITE; /*!40000 ALTER TABLE `tours` DISABLE KEYS */; INSERT INTO `tours` VALUES (1,'Borobudur Sunrise Tour','borobudur-sunrise-tour','<p>Experience the magic of <strong>Borobudur at sunrise</strong> on this early-morning guided tour. Watch the first light illuminate the ancient stupas as mist rolls over the surrounding jungles and volcanoes.</p>\n<h4>Highlights</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Exclusive sunrise access before public opening</li>\n<li>Professional English-speaking local guide</li>\n<li>Hotel pickup and drop-off in Yogyakarta</li>\n<li>Visit to Mendut and Pawon temples en route</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Itinerary</h4>\n<p>03:30 AM hotel pickup, 04:30 AM arrival at the sunrise viewpoint, 06:00 AM explore the temple reliefs with your guide, 08:00 AM return transfer. Duration approximately 5 hours.</p>\n<h4>What to Bring</h4>\n<p>Warm jacket (mornings are cool), comfortable walking shoes, camera, and a respectful attitude as this is an active religious site.</p>','Saksikan keindahan sunrise di Candi Borobudur yang megah','template/assets/images/travel-list/1.jpg',350000.00,275000.00,1,0,20,'Borobudur, Magelang','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Cultural','Bestseller',4.90,128,1,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 09:04:29'),(2,'Prambanan Temple Tour','prambanan-temple-tour','<p>Discover the grandeur of <strong>Prambanan Temple</strong>, Indonesia\'s largest Hindu temple complex, on this half-day cultural tour from Yogyakarta.</p>\n<h4>Highlights</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Guided walk through the Trimurti temples</li>\n<li>Storytelling of the Ramayana relief panels</li>\n<li>Optional Ramayana Ballet evening show</li>\n<li>Hotel pickup and drop-off included</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Itinerary</h4>\n<p>Morning or afternoon departure, guided exploration of the main complex and museum, free time for photos, and return transfer. Duration approximately 4 hours.</p>\n<h4>Good to Know</h4>\n<p>Dress modestly and wear a sarong (provided at entrance). The site involves walking and stairs; bring water and sun protection.</p>','Kunjungi kompleks candi Hindu terbesar di Indonesia','template/assets/images/travel-list/2.jpg',250000.00,200000.00,1,0,30,'Prambanan, Sleman','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Cultural','Popular',4.80,95,1,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 09:04:29'),(3,'Jomblang Cave Adventure','jomblang-cave-adventure','Petualangan seru ke Gua Jomblang yang menakjubkan. Turun ke dalam gua dengan teknik rappelling.','Petualangan seru ke gua dengan cahaya alami yang spektakuler','template/assets/images/travel-list/3.jpg',450000.00,375000.00,1,0,15,'Gunung Kidul','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Adventure','Trending',4.70,76,1,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(4,'Parangtritis Beach Tour','parangtritis-beach-tour','<p>Escape the city and feel the ocean breeze on this relaxing <strong>Parangtritis Beach</strong> tour, combining natural beauty with Javanese mythology.</p>\n<h4>Highlights</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Scenic drive through villages south of Yogyakarta</li>\n<li>Black-sand beach and dramatic coastline</li>\n<li>Optional horseback ride along the shore</li>\n<li>Visit to the Parangtritis Geomaritime Science Park</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Itinerary</h4>\n<p>Afternoon pickup, sunset viewing at the beach, local seafood dinner, and return in the evening. Duration approximately 5 hours.</p>','Eksplor pantai vulkanik dengan sunset yang memukau','template/assets/images/travel-list/4.jpg',200000.00,150000.00,1,0,25,'Parangtritis, Bantul','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Nature','Hot Deal',4.60,112,1,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 09:04:29'),(5,'Malioboro City Tour','malioboro-city-tour','Jelajahi jantung kota Yogyakarta di Jalan Malioboro. Belanja oleh-oleh dan nikmati kuliner khas.','Eksplor jantung kota Yogyakarta yang ikonik','template/assets/images/travel-list/5.jpg',150000.00,100000.00,1,0,40,'Malioboro, Yogyakarta','Yogyakarta',NULL,'City Tour','Bestseller',4.50,203,1,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(6,'Kidul Mountain Tour','kidul-mountain-tour','<p>Venture into the lush southern highlands on the <strong>Gunung Kidul</strong> adventure tour, where limestone hills, hidden caves, and pristine beaches await.</p>\n<h4>Highlights</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Exploration of karst caves and underground rivers</li>\n<li>Swimming in natural pools and waterfalls</li>\n<li>Visit to traditional villages</li>\n<li>Panoramic views from the limestone plateau</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Itinerary</h4>\n<p>Full-day tour with hotel pickup, multiple stops across the Gunung Kidul region, local lunch, and return transfer. Duration approximately 8-9 hours.</p>','Eksplor keindahan pantai selatan Gunung Kidul','template/assets/images/travel-list/6.jpg',300000.00,250000.00,2,1,20,'Gunung Kidul','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Nature','Adventure',4.70,89,0,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 09:04:29'),(7,'Imogiri Royal Cemetery Tour','imogiri-royal-cemetery-tour','Kunjungi Makam Raja-raja Mataram di Imogiri. Pelajari sejarah kerajaan Jawa.','Wisata sejarah ke makam raja-raja Mataram','template/assets/images/travel-list/7.jpg',175000.00,125000.00,1,0,25,'Imogiri, Bantul','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Cultural','Heritage',4.40,67,0,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'),(8,'Pindul Cave Tubing','pindul-cave-tubing','Sensasi cave tubing di Gua Pindul yang menyenangkan dengan ban pelampung.','Sensasi cave tubing di gua bawah tanah','template/assets/images/travel-list/8.jpg',200000.00,150000.00,1,0,15,'Gunung Kidul','Yogyakarta',NULL,'Adventure','Fun',4.60,145,0,1,'2026-07-09 00:15:27','2026-07-09 00:15:27'); /*!40000 ALTER TABLE `tours` ENABLE KEYS */; UNLOCK TABLES;  -- -- Table structure for table `use